emotions.name: Embarrassment
emotions.quote: She had instinctively turned away; but stopping on his approach, received his compliments with an embarrassment impossible to be overcome.

causedBy.description: Seeing Mr. Darcy unexpectedly at Pemberley

emotions.name: Gratitude
emotions.quote: she thought of his regard with a deeper sentiment of gratitude than it had ever raised before

causedBy.description: Praise of Mr. Darcy by the housekeeper

emotions.name: Shame
emotions.quote: She was overpowered by shame and vexation.

causedBy.description: Unexpected meeting with Mr. Darcy at Pemberley

emotions.name: Curiosity
emotions.quote: she longed to know what at that moment was passing in his mind

causedBy.description: Unexpected meeting with Mr. Darcy at Pemberley
